blog.title: Haida, That Guy Who Has That Crush On Retsuko...
blog.description: (This is an aggretsuko ask blog, come drop by and leave an ask!) hey there, you probably know who I am..that one hyena who has a crush on a particular someone..(and heh if I you’re gonna ask nsfw questions, please nothing too obscene) (Header art by; Blue-chica)

summary: Hey Haida, how's it going?  Hope work hasn't been too hard on you.  With all that work you do, have you ever thought of escaping...
question: Hey Haida, how's it going?  Hope work hasn't been too hard on you.  With all that work you do, have you ever thought of escaping somewhere free from all that stress?  If so, where would you go?
answer: “It’s been going ok, same old same old..I don’t know where I’d go honestly. I wouldn’t want to go anywhere alone if I’m being honest, I’d want someone with me…”

Usually Ookami bends down to let Tamara kiss him but this time Tam has decided to try and reach him herself. Standing on her tip toes she was able to give him a quick kiss before landing back down on her feet.

Ships with a height difference one of my weakness
